  <div>● <strong style="color:#9db4f0">Live banner</strong>: pinned at top when saved teams are playing — auto-shows/hides</div>
  <div>● <strong style="color:#9db4f0">Segment control</strong>: Teams / Competitions / Players — iOS-style pill switcher</div>
