# Project Overview - Quick Score

## Product Description
Quick Score is a React Native mobile app for live football scores, fixtures, standings, and match details. Competitor to Flashscore, FotMob, SofaScore.

## MVP Scope (Phase 1)
**Focus:** Football only. Multi-league from day 1 (top 5 European leagues + domestic competitions).

### Core Features
- Live scores with real-time updates (2-5s cadence)
- Match detail: lineups, event timeline (goals/cards/subs), stats
- League standings (live table updates)
- Fixtures (upcoming 7 days + today)
- Favorites: save teams and competitions
- Push notifications: goal alerts, red cards, match start

### Out of Scope (Phase 2+)
- Video highlights
- Betting odds
- Player tracking
- News integration
- Smartwatch support

## Target Users
Sports fans who want fast, reliable live football scores on mobile.

## Platform
- iOS (primary)
- Android (secondary)
- Web (via Expo Router, future)

## Data Source
API-Football (free tier): 2000+ leagues, real-time data, no credit card required.
